Subject: Re: [T2] valve adjustment

I have a piece of 1x4 I ground down so it just fits between the top edge 
of the valve cover and the engine floor above it- to prevent the valve 
cover from sliding off the head as the bale is pried up. Greasing the 
area the bale wire rubs on helps also.
